Package: TrendUtilities
Type: Package
Title: Utility functions to generate Bayesian response-randomized trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Massimiliano Russo
Maintainer: Massimiliano Russo <m_russo@hms.harvard.edu>
Description: Function to simulate Bayesian response multi-arm and platform trials. Function for platform trial simulations are  based on the R  ones available package AddArmsToTrial by Steffen Venz, with sometimes minimal variations. Refer to specific function for details.  
